{"tid":543870,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"傳新東再有DQ 陳國強：選舉主任日日偷睇我FB","createTime":"2018-01-29T03:18:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-29T04:16:53.000Z","uid":79563,"like":35,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"1f2a88683fb0da568f6a48ce9aec77a2eb3d4de6","tid":543870,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T03:18:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180129/large/1517193680_6289.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180129%2Flarge%2F1517193680_6289.jpg&h=5d30b3ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2016年政府DQ包括梁天琦、陳浩天等多名本土派參選人，同年梁頌恆、游蕙禎因宣誓案被法院DQ，去年4名民主派議員再被DQ。日前政府再以香港眾志綱領倡議民主自決為藉口，進行政治審查，DQ眾志常委周庭，剝奪周參加立法會港島區補選的資格。補選提名期今日結束，姚松炎屬被DQ「高危」人士外，新東的社區網絡聯盟前召集人劉頴匡以及沙田區議員陳國強，至今亦未被確認參選資格，有傳2人會被DQ。"},{"pid":"8d0cbb3a2d6d8ac5b21cbba2809441f2f083605d","tid":543870,"uid":49955,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T03:19:18.000Z","msg":"識玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24e85686fc5e9b67908b37326c9e7d9e232d5d2c","tid":543870,"uid":79563,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"8d0cbb3a2d6d8ac5b21cbba2809441f2f083605d","tid":543870,"uid":49955,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T03:19:18.000Z","msg":"識玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T03:20:19.000Z","msg":"識玩就張本基本法放上神枱<br />\n<br />\n為本基本法裝香<br />\n<br />\n再影張相放上FB比選舉主任睇"},{"pid":"0c657eb2f6dfee82333012dc7648e4fcd1f64283","tid":543870,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T03:21:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a2ddba7a7183601eb194c47fb4854cc5b207d66","tid":543870,"uid":49955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T03:23:58.00